{"id":4133,"date":"2025-06-14T14:50:10","date_gmt":"2025-06-14T07:50:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4133"},"modified":"2025-06-14T14:50:10","modified_gmt":"2025-06-14T07:50:10","slug":"tay-da-chet-han-quoc-tot-nhat","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/tay-da-chet-han-quoc-tot-nhat\/","title":{"rendered":"Top 10 t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho da m\u1eb7t"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u t\u00edn \u0111\u1ed3 skincare nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean gi\u00fap b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o, h\u1ea5p thu d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng \u2013 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn. Mang \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch t\u1ed1i \u01b0u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay top t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"san-pham-tay-da-chet-han-quoc-tot-nhat-co-that-su-dang-thu\"><\/span><b>S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1eed?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gel<\/span><b> t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da. M\u00e0 c\u00f2n mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i cho l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng. H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1ea5p thu d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, an to\u00e0n cho da: H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng<\/span><b> t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft m\u1eb7t <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 b\u1ea3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh. Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 tr\u00e0 xanh, hoa c\u00fac, enzyme tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y\u2026 Gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf da ch\u1ebft m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, gi\u00fap da th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng: S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba. M\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en v\u00e0 m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m v\u00e0 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u00e0n da: Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch, c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft m\u1eb7t H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f2n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m nh\u01b0 HA, glycerin gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da, ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a: T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean gi\u00fap k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da. T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ea3n sinh collagen, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng. V\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c ti\u1ebfp theo.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"top-10-kem-tay-da-chet-han-quoc-tot-nhat-cho-da-mat\"><\/span><b>Top 10 kem t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho da m\u1eb7t<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m <\/span><b>t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng. V\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c ti\u1ebfp theo. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng <\/span><b>t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft cho da kh\u00f4<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> v\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1edd th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-natural-peeling-%e2%80%93-kem-tay-da-chet-sinh-hoc-an-toan-cho-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC Natural Peeling \u2013 Kem t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc an to\u00e0n cho da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC Natural Peeling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng <\/span><b>t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc. Gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng hay l\u00e0m m\u1ecfng da. V\u1edbi chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb enzym \u0111u \u0111\u1ee7 (Papain). s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da m\u00e0 v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 pH t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4121\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4121\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4121\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-2.webp\" alt=\"GSC Natural Peeling\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4121\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GSC Natural Peeling<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh v\u1edbi chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7n t\u00e2y, b\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i xanh, c\u00e0 r\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1eadu n\u00e0nh, h\u1ea1t lanh, l\u00f4 h\u1ed9i, hoa sen, l\u00e1 \u0111ay\u2026 gi\u00fap nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng enzym tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da, kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Duy tr\u00ec h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng, s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"laneige-multiberry-yogurt-peeling-gel-%e2%80%93-tay-da-chet-diu-nhe-huong-dau-tuoi-mat\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Laneige Multiberry Yogurt Peeling Gel \u2013 T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, h\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2u t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u00e1t<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Laneige Multiberry Yogurt Peeling Gel l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng <\/span><b>t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft cho da kh\u00f4<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t. Gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p enzyme t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean t\u1eeb c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3 m\u1ecdng. K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng AHA v\u00e0 BHA gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da s\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c h\u1ea1t vi sinh gi\u00fap t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y ma s\u00e1t m\u1ea1nh tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 nam vi\u1ec7t qu\u1ea5t, vi\u1ec7t qu\u1ea5t, d\u00e2u t\u00e2y, m\u00e2m x\u00f4i, c\u00e2u k\u1ef7 t\u1eed gi\u00fap cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u00f9i h\u01b0\u01a1ng sinh t\u1ed1 d\u00e2u s\u1eefa chua mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4122\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4122\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4122\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-3.webp\" alt=\"Laneige Multiberry Yogurt Peeling Gel\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4122\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Laneige Multiberry Yogurt Peeling Gel<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"innisfree-green-barley-gommage-peeling-mask-%e2%80%93-tay-te-bao-chet-thien-nhien-tu-lua-mach\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Innisfree Green Barley Gommage Peeling Mask \u2013 T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean t\u1eeb l\u00faa m\u1ea1ch<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n thu\u1ea7n thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, Innisfree Green Barley Gommage Peeling Mask l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t l\u00faa m\u1ea1ch c\u00f9ng ba lo\u1ea1i AHA t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p AHA t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean gi\u00fap da s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u00e0o m\u00f2n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9a g\u1ea1o, v\u1ecf qu\u00fdt gi\u00fap b\u1ed5 sung th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4123\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4123\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4123\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-4.webp\" alt=\"Innisfree Green Barley Gommage Peeling Mask\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4123\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Innisfree Green Barley Gommage Peeling Mask<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dabo-peeling-gel-%e2%80%93-tay-te-bao-chet-da-nang-cho-mat-co-the\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Dabo Peeling Gel \u2013 T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft \u0111a n\u0103ng cho m\u1eb7t &amp; c\u01a1 th\u1ec3<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Dabo Peeling Gel l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i da v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho c\u1ea3 m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng da s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i. Nh\u01b0 khu\u1ef7u tay, \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, g\u00f3t ch\u00e2n<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4124\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4124\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4124\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-5.webp\" alt=\"Dabo Peeling Gel\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4124\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dabo Peeling Gel<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u00fap da s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 t\u1ed1i \u0111a.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u00edch th\u00edch da \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi, t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o, gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ohui-clear-science-soft-peeling-%e2%80%93-gel-tay-te-bao-chet-diu-nhe-tu-thien-nhien\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ohui Clear Science Soft Peeling \u2013 Gel t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 t\u1eeb thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ohui Clear Science Soft Peeling l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cao c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u OHUI. V\u1edbi c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c an to\u00e0n, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p ngay c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4125\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4125\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4125\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-6.webp\" alt=\"Ohui Clear Science Soft Peeling \" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-6.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-6-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-6-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-6-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4125\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ohui Clear Science Soft Peeling<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ee9a chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb rong bi\u1ec3n v\u00e0 tr\u00e0 xanh. K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p enzyme t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean gi\u00fap t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c h\u1ea1t gel si\u00eau nh\u1ecf gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. Ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en, m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho da, gi\u00fap da m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huxley-scrub-mask-%e2%80%93-giai-phap-tay-da-chet-diu-nhe-tu-xuong-rong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Huxley Scrub Mask \u2013 Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 t\u1eeb x\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ed3ng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m <\/span><b>t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> d\u00e0nh cho l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, Huxley Scrub Mask s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4126\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4126\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4126\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-7.webp\" alt=\"Huxley Scrub Mask\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-7.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-7-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-7-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-7-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4126\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Huxley Scrub Mask<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ee9a chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t x\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ed3ng gi\u00fap l\u1ea5y \u0111i t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 h\u1ea1t \u00f3c ch\u00f3 xay nhuy\u1ec5n. Gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m t\u1ee9c th\u00ec v\u1edbi chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t rong bi\u1ec3n v\u00e0 d\u01b0a chu\u1ed9t. Gi\u00fap da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng sau khi t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cosrx-bha-blackhead-power-liquid-%e2%80%93-tay-te-bao-chet-hoa-hoc-chuyen-sau\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cosrx BHA Blackhead Power Liquid \u2013 T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cosrx BHA Blackhead Power Liquid l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc d\u1ea1ng l\u1ecfng. Gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4127\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4127\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4127\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-8.webp\" alt=\"Cosrx BHA Blackhead Power Liquid\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-8.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-8-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-8-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-8-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4127\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cosrx BHA Blackhead Power Liquid<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ee9a 4% BHA gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba, b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en v\u00e0 m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t v\u1ecf c\u00e2y li\u1ec5u tr\u1eafng gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da. Gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"some-by-mi-yuja-niacin-%e2%80%93-tay-te-bao-chet-duong-trang-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Some By Mi Yuja Niacin \u2013 T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Some By Mi Yuja Niacin l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. D\u00e0nh cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u. M\u00e0 v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean tr\u00ean da. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean an to\u00e0n. Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4128\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4128\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4128\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-9.webp\" alt=\"Some By Mi Yuja Niacin\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-9.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-9-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-9-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-9-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4128\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Some By Mi Yuja Niacin<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa PHA v\u00e0 cellulose gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">PHA h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc, gi\u00fap da c\u0103ng m\u1ecbn, gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u m\u1ee5n c\u00e1m, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t Yuja, niacinamide v\u00e0 h\u01a1n 10 lo\u1ea1i vitamin gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da, gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"the-face-shop-smart-peeling-white-jewel-%e2%80%93-tay-te-bao-chet-tu-ngoc-trai\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The Face Shop Smart Peeling White Jewel \u2013 T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u1eeb ng\u1ecdc trai<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The Face Shop Smart Peeling White Jewel l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u1eeba t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft v\u1eeba gi\u00fap d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng da t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4129\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4129\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4129\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-10.webp\" alt=\"The Face Shop Smart Peeling White Jewel\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-10.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-10-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-10-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-10-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4129\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Face Shop Smart Peeling White Jewel<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9a b\u1ed9t ng\u1ecdc trai, \u0111\u00e1 m\u1eaft m\u00e8o v\u00e0 th\u1ea1ch anh t\u00edm. Gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch l\u1edbp s\u1eebng b\u00e1m tr\u00ean da, gi\u00fap da th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng, s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da, gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u, ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"g9-skin-grapefruit-vita-peeling-gel-%e2%80%93-tay-da-chet-diu-nhe-tu-buoi\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">G9 Skin GrapeFruit Vita Peeling Gel \u2013 T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 t\u1eeb b\u01b0\u1edfi<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">G9 Skin GrapeFruit Vita Peeling Gel l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. Nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c nh\u1eb9 d\u1ecbu nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t b\u01b0\u1edfi gi\u00e0u Vitamin C, gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft. C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n l\u00e0n da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">AHA, BHA gi\u00fap ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u, kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4130\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4130\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4130\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-11.webp\" alt=\"G9 Skin GrapeFruit Vita Peeling Gel\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-11.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-11-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-11-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/49-11-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4130\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">G9 Skin GrapeFruit Vita Peeling Gel<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-chon-gel-tay-te-bao-chet-han-quoc-phu-hop\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn gel t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uu-tien-thanh-phan-diu-nhe-an-toan-cho-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u01afu ti\u00ean th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, an to\u00e0n cho da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp s\u1eebng gi\u00e0 c\u1ed7i. M\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n cho l\u00e0n da. Khi ch\u1ecdn gel t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean. Ch\u1ee9a enzyme t\u1eeb tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y ho\u1eb7c acid d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 nh\u01b0 AHA, BHA. \u0110\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. Tr\u00e1nh xa c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 h\u1ea1t t\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n. V\u00ec ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai c\u00f3 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chon-san-pham-phu-hop-voi-tung-loai-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i gel t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da d\u1ea7u, h\u00e3y t\u00ecm s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn. V\u1edbi da kh\u00f4, \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh bong tr\u00f3c. Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u hay ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u00e0u. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1eb7t, vi\u1ec7c <\/span><b>t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft da \u0111\u1ea7u<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4092\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4092\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4092\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-5.webp\" alt=\"GSC Natural Peeling c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4092\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GSC Natural Peeling c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lua-chon-thuong-hieu-uy-tin-de-dam-bao-chat-luong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u uy t\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng phong ph\u00fa. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng h\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3, h\u00e0ng k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00e0n lan. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn mua gel t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang quy tr\u00ecnh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc hay r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t s\u1ea1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n. Sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi d\u00f9ng gel t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn <\/span><b>t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. H\u00e3y \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m an to\u00e0n, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean th\u1eed ngay c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe l\u00e0n da. Ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng ng\u1eddi!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay top t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4131,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4133","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4133","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4133"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4133\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4134,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4133\/revisions\/4134"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4131"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4133"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4133"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4133"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}